layout: layouts/_base.njk
title: 2020 Conference - RadicalxChange
gitxchange: |
  Ahead of the conference, we are hosting a two-week virtual hackathon together with Gitcoin to further develop tools for bottom-up experimentation with radical political economies. The hackathon includes a variety of challenges ranging from coding and designing to conceptualizing ideas about cooperative plurality. Winning projects will present their creations on the virtual conference stage.

  The sponsoring teams include [Democracy Earth](https://democracy.earth/), [Idena](https://idena.io/), [Gitcoin](http://www.gitcoin.co/), [Ocean Protocol](https://oceanprotocol.com/), [The Scheme of Things](https://rijeka2020.eu/en/dogadjanja/the-scheme-of-things-jennifer-lyn-morone-us/), [Wildcards](https://wildcards.world/), and [RadicalxChange Foundation](https://www.radicalxchange.org/).
sponsors:
